  "title": "Engineer (Technical Support)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Salary:</strong> $3000 - $5000<br /><strong>Working Hours:</strong> Mon–Fri, 9:00 am – 6:00 pm<br /><strong>Location:</strong> Kaki Bukit</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare technical proposals/tender submissions (compliance matrix, datasheets) and review specs/drawings for alignment.</p></li><li><p>Support solution design: site surveys, technical evaluations, product selection, BOM preparation, and client presentations.</p></li><li><p>Execute testing/commissioning and troubleshoot hardware/software issues; propose alternative solutions when needed.</p></li><li><p>Maintain technical documentation (incident reports, equipment records, maintenance logs) and system databases/compliance trackers; conduct product training.</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with Sales/Engineering/PMO, attend technical meetings, and support product improvements.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor’s in Mechanical/Electrical Engineering (or related).</p></li><li><p>Preferably 2+ years in HVAC/BMS/CRAC/building systems technical support.</p></li><li><p>Working knowledge of AutoCAD/BIM for drawing review.</p></li><li><p>Strong understanding of M&E systems and engineering fundamentals.</p></li></ul><p><strong>How to Apply</strong><br />Submit your CV via “Apply Now” or text <strong>+65 9422 1220</strong> for a confidential discussion.</p><p>Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>MTC Consulting Pte Ltd | 15C7752<br />EA Reg. No.: R22111807 | Yap Teng Hui</p>",
